				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">People have talked about it in another thread ... the command : 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">/pet report health </span>
<br />

<br />
(<span style="font-weight: bold">/pet health</span> only may work)
<br />

<br />
gives you the percentage of pet life left, aswell as all buffs / debuffs on him. Very useful when you missed the "Your pet's Burnout X spell has worn off" <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381021" target="_blank" class="postlink">Majax Lotz</a>
